title: music taste aside, what font is this?
content:
Can anyone identify the font used on [www.cowboytroy.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20060716120427/http:/www.cowboytroy.com/) (the nav and titles)? I know there are TONS of western themed fonts and ones that look similar to it, but I can’t seem to find this exact font.

Anyone know it?
author: efthomas
